«c1»This is a NEW creation in D.I.S.C.  Before all these articles would have
been placed in the Scene section. Anyway, the following articles deal with
escential topics and are perhaps the most special articles in D.I.S.C.«»
«»
This time we have tried to cover the the entire history of the amiga and
the scene, we are predicting the future of the amiga and the scene,
we are looking at the 100 best games ever, we are introducing a new
prestigious scene prize, we have a competition with a prize, we have scene
reports from some of the most active scene-countries and some articles from
sceners looking back at their careers. The following articles are written
by Darkhawk, Zerox, Punisher and Splatterhead. And we just have to mention
that one of the articles is the biggest ever published in a scene
publication. Enjoy it!«»
